    "description": "You play the role of a gravedigger who takes care of peace and order at the cemetery every day. Your daytime duties seem simple, but they require attention and commitment<br><br>However, when darkness falls, the cemetery comes to life in a completely different way. The night brings unexpected challenges – things you don't expect. Every night can surprise you, and you have to be ready to face whatever has decided to go out for an evening walk.<br><br><br>Driving a Melex around the cemetery is not just ordinary transport - time is running out and there are plenty of responsibilities. Sometimes you have to be in a hurry, which means that slightly damaging a tombstone is just... part of the workday. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301350/extras/19d64bd0a669a89be865a3d171cd4196.poster.avif?t=1764253088\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301350/extras/19d64bd0a669a89be865a3d171cd4196.webm?t=1764253088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Assembling coffins is the basis of every day - each one must be carefully prepared, because we never know what we will use it for in the end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301350/extras/ade774f988db9a731edd3df3ea1e1683.poster.avif?t=1764253088\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301350/extras/ade774f988db9a731edd3df3ea1e1683.webm?t=1764253088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Sometimes the situation at the cemetery requires more than just a shovel and a melex. When things start to get out of control, you need to reinforce yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301350/extras/8ddf7dbd3f8ec019a8c5f33f4aa70b9c.poster.avif?t=1764253088\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301350/extras/8ddf7dbd3f8ec019a8c5f33f4aa70b9c.webm?t=1764253088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>When the dead decide to leave their graves, your task is clear: gently but firmly guide them back to their resting place. Peace must be restored!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301350/extras/391a216ec41da18a65782b4b795adc51.poster.avif?t=1764253088\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301350/extras/391a216ec41da18a65782b4b795adc51.webm?t=1764253088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Remember that as a gravedigger you have to be ready for anything.",
